00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:30,750
Juanjuan.

295
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,880
I just arrived.

296
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:33,790
I didn't expect the signal in the mountain to be so bad.

297
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:35,720
