302
00:17:42,310 --> 00:17:43,070
Don't worry.

303
00:17:46,270 --> 00:17:47,510
I'm on my way.

304
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:49,550
It's very cold in the mountain.

305
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:50,960
And...

306
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:55,310
And I sneaked out.

307
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,400
I didn't tell my teacher.

308
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:59,440
So I have to hurry.

309
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:01,240
