310
00:18:01,750 --> 00:18:02,830
Wait for me.

311
00:18:02,830 --> 00:18:04,240
Juanjuan, good morning.

312
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:05,590
It's 5:00 in the morning.

313
00:18:05,590 --> 00:18:06,480
I just got up.

314
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,720
It rained halfway yesterday.

315
00:18:09,790 --> 00:18:11,550
The rain came fast in the mountain.

316
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:15,640
I didn't want to trouble the villagers and my teacher.

317
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:16,960
So I came back.

318
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:19,160
But when I arrive in town this afternoon,

319
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:21,750
