320
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:25,440
Three, two, one.

321
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:26,750
It's 0:00 now.

322
00:18:26,790 --> 00:18:28,790
It's Jiang Juanjuan's birthday.

323
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,880
Happy birthday to you, Jiang Juanjuan.

324
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:35,830
Today is your first birthday after we've been together.

325
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:37,640
I'm sorry.

326
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:39,680
I can't go to Yunhai to accompany you.

327
00:18:40,270 --> 00:18:42,550
Juanjuan, do you remember the tellurion I gave you

328
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:43,880
when I graduated?

329
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:47,640
The coordinates under it are the location of Heart Island.

330
00:18:49,070 --> 00:18:52,070
Humans found Heart Island

331
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:53,270
on the Earth of five trillion square kilometers.

332
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:56,000
There are seven billion people on the Earth.

333
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:58,030
I only found you.

334
00:18:58,720 --> 00:19:01,270
I'm very lucky to meet you, Jiang Juanjuan.

335
00:19:02,310 --> 00:19:03,480
Happy birthday to you.

336
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,590
Let me sing you a birthday song.

337
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:09,640
Happy birthday to you.

338
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:14,510
It's late. Everyone's asleep.

339
00:19:15,030 --> 00:19:16,030
I should go to bed too.

340
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:17,400
You should rest early too.

341
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:18,680
Jiang Juanjuan.

342
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:19,680
Good night.

343
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,720
Sorry.

344
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:29,440
Screw you.

345
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:33,750
I apologize.

346
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:35,680
Don't think I don't know

347
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:37,920
"apologize" and "sorry"

348
00:19:38,030 --> 00:19:40,070
have similar meanings.

349
00:19:40,270 --> 00:19:41,070
What's going on?

350
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:45,000
You being happy

351
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:47,310
is the most important to me.

352
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,350
Instead of explaining and quibbling,

353
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,590
I'd rather spend time making you happy.

354
00:19:53,590 --> 00:19:55,160
You can complain.

355
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:57,240
I won't think you're immature or unreasonable.

356
00:19:58,030 --> 00:19:59,790
So you don't have to care about my feelings.

357
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:03,550
I'm happy when you're happy.

358
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:13,480
What you said is useless.

359
00:20:15,270 --> 00:20:16,510
Let me ask you,

360
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:23,750
