367
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,310
I wanted to give you a surprise.

368
00:21:47,030 --> 00:21:48,550
Are you cleaning?

369
00:21:48,550 --> 00:21:49,440
Yes.

370
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:51,400
I thought you haven't been home for a long time.

371
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:52,640
So I should do some cleaning.

372
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:54,400
And the two families can have dinner together.

373
00:21:55,590 --> 00:21:56,310
You're back.

374
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:57,590
We're back.

375
00:21:58,830 --> 00:21:59,640
Let me help you.

376
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:00,440
No need.

377
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:01,400
You just came back.

378
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:02,440
Get some rest.

379
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:03,880
Chao, hurry up.

380
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:04,510
Take a rest.

381
00:22:19,070 --> 00:22:21,200
Why haven't I seen these photos before?

382
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:24,590
When did you eat cakes behind my back?

383
00:22:24,790 --> 00:22:26,030
You ate them too.

384
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:28,310
I didn't eat too many.

385
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:45,350
